"Respecting and protecting the legitimate rights and interests of user information is Lenovo's consistent system. Users approve Lenovo to take the following approach to handle user information:
"

"According to the product features, and approved by users, Lenovo may collect the following data:
"

"To pay return visits for users' feedbacks or in the case that users participate in activities, it might be possible to ask the users to input or report their information of phone numbers and email addresses, etc.;
"

"Cameras (front and rear) and microphone will be called after the starting of the software to realize video call function;
"

"Some basic record information and its related information explicitly and objectively reflected on the server end of Lenovo such as users' operating states and use behavioral information of the software, for example: phone IMEI, software usage, software upgrade request information, user-requested information or account synchronization and users' geographic information when logging into the software, etc. n "

"After installation, Youyue will analyze your phone contacts after your permission to help you find your friends who are already using Youyue. Youyue encrypts your phone number by using a high-intensity and irreversible encryption algorithm (encrypts collected number to a series of un-decryptable strings) and retrieve the phone numbers on your phone book to check if their encrypted strings are consistent with the one-way encrypted strings of the existing users' phone numbers in Youyue. If consistent, the other party may be a friend you know. Other users can also use their phone contacts to find you and contact with you.n "

"Lenovo allows you to download and use Youyue;
"
"Lenovo (and its authorizer, if any) owns all rights, titles and interests of this website and Yonyou, including related intellectual property rights, but excluding your user content.n "
